  </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Thorn Mail (n00b HFL Ranger Armor from MT)</span><hr size=1> Last patch added some noobie armor quests for Halflings in RV.  MT was also changed fairly drastically along with some missing trades kill vendors added in RV.<br>
<br>
Thorn Mail = n00b Halfling Ranger Armor<br>
<br>
